# Gibbon ERP Backend Integration & Deployment Plan

## Executive Summary

**Project**: Integrate Gibbon Education Platform v31.0.00 as production backend for college website  
**Hosting**: Hostinger shared hosting  
**Database**: Existing MySQL database (`u542293952_productionldm`)  
**Status**: ✅ **Compatible with Modifications**

