## 1️⃣ PROJECT AUDIT

### System Identified
- **Name**: Gibbon Education Platform
- **Version**: 31.0.00
- **Type**: Open-source School/College ERP & LMS
- **License**: GNU GPL v3.0
- **Official Site**: https://gibbonedu.org

### Technology Stack

#### Backend
- **Language**: PHP
- **Required Version**: PHP 8.0+ (`^8.0`)
- **Framework**: Custom MVC with modern components
  - Slim Framework 4.0 (routing)
  - Twig 3.3 (templating)
  - League Container 3.3 (dependency injection)
  - Monolog (logging)

#### Required PHP Extensions
```
✓ ext-curl      (HTTP requests)
✓ ext-intl      (Internationalization)
✓ ext-mbstring  (Multi-byte strings)
✓ ext-gettext   (Translations)
✓ ext-PDO       (Database)
✓ ext-gd        (Image processing - not in composer but needed)
✓ ext-zip       (File handling - not in composer but needed)
```

#### Database
- **Type**: MySQL/MariaDB
- **Tables**: 100+ tables
- **Schema Size**: 521 KB SQL file
- **Key Features**:
  - Student enrollment & management
  - Teacher & staff management
  - Course & class management
  - Attendance tracking
  - Timetable system
  - Behavior tracking
  - Reporting & analytics
  - Parent portal
  - Admissions system
  - Finance/billing module
  - Library management

#### Dependencies (25+ packages)
**Critical Dependencies**:
- Google API Client 2.2+
- PHPMailer 6.5+
- TCPDF 6.4+ (PDF generation)
- PHPSpreadsheet 1.29+ (Excel)
- mPDF 8.2+ (PDF reports)
- Omnipay (payment integration)

